+-------------+---------+
| Column Name | Type    |
+-------------+---------+
| personId    | int     |
| lastName    | varchar |
| firstName   | varchar |
+-------------+---------+
personId is the primary key column for this table.
This table contains information about the ID of some persons and their first and last names.





=============================================================================
SELECT
    firstName,
    lastName,
    city,
    state
FROM
    Person AS p
    LEFT JOIN Address AS a ON p.personId = a.personId;
